A colossal elephant standing confidently atop a tiny glass marble balanced on a needle point, set against a dramatic stormy sky with lightning in the background, the elephant appears relaxed and stable despite the impossible physics, the marble glows with an inner amber light, photorealistic style with hyper-detailed elephant skin texture and realistic storm clouds, cinematic lighting with the elephant silhouetted against purple and orange storm clouds, conveying the paradox of unexpected strength and capability defying assumptions about what can support massive weight.
